--------
SAM LAWS
----

	This file contains a list of desired ranges for Sam's movement
abilities.

    - Sam's jump should take him 6 and a half tiles off the ground from
which he jumps.

    - Sam should be able to clear a 13 tile gap with a maximum running
jump.

    - Sam should be able to wall jump easily up a shaft that is 9
tiles wide.

    - Falling a distance less than 20 tiles will not hurt Sam.
  
    - Sam can fit under a 3 tile high gap when ducking, allowing for
duckslide on ice under 3 tile high gaps.